title: SC EP:137 After Hours Conversation
itunes:title: SC EP:137 After Hours Conversation
description:
Tonight is an after hours conversation with a Joe who is a listener to the show. Tomorrow night Woody and I interview Brandon who has a lot of activity on and around his property.

Tonight we speak to Joe who brought a great topic up about Sasquatch origins. Sit back and relax as the three of us have a conversation about Sasquatch.
